      <title>日产计划到 2027 年推出 30 款新车型，提升全球销量</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/nissan-targets-1-mln-vehicle-sales-growth-over-next-three-years-2024-03-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日产汽车周一表示，将在未来三年内推出 30 款新车型，目标是将全球销量增加 100 万辆，同时削减成本以提高盈利能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/nissan-targets-1-mln-vehicle-sales-growth-over-next-three-years-2024-03-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 06:26:35 GMT</pubDate>
